---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import myImage from "../assets/about.jpg";
import SectionTitle from "./SectionTitle.astro";
---

<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24" id="about">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start">
      <!-- Image Container - Takes 5 columns -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:sticky lg:top-24">
        <div class="relative mx-auto lg:mx-0">
          <div class="aspect-[4/5]">
            <Image
              src={myImage}
              alt="Jake Meyers - Full Stack & AI Developer"
              class="rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
            />
          </div>
          <div
            class="absolute -z-10 -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-2xl opacity-70 blur-2xl"
          >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Text Container - Takes 7 columns -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 space-y-8">
        <SectionTitle title="About" />
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Welcome to Gateway Digital Studio, your comprehensive technology partner based in St. Louis, Missouri. We specialize in both artificial intelligence solutions and web development, serving businesses of all sizes, from local enterprises to Fortune 500 companies across the globe.
          </p>
  
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Our Expertise</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 mt-1 mr-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">AI Solutions:</strong> From RAG applications and intelligent agents to custom chatbots that enhance customer service and streamline operations.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 mt-1 mr-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">Web Development:</strong> Full-stack applications, CMS websites, e-commerce solutions, and custom web platforms tailored to your needs.
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center w-6 h-6 mt-1 mr-3 bg-blue-100 rounded-full">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <span>
                <strong class="text-gray-900">E-commerce:</strong> Shopify store development, payment integrations, and comprehensive online retail solutions.
              </span>
            </li>
          </ul>
  
          <p class="mt-8">
            Founded by Jake Meyers, a full-stack developer and AI consultant, we bring together technical expertise with innovative solutions to drive your business forward. Our dual focus on web development and AI technology allows us to create integrated solutions that not only meet today's needs but anticipate tomorrow's challenges.
          </p>
  
          <p class="mt-4">
            While we're proudly rooted in St. Louis, Missouri, our services extend to clients worldwide. At Gateway Digital Studio, we maintain a boutique approach, providing the personalized attention of a small agency while delivering enterprise-grade solutions across both web development and AI integration.
          </p>
  
          <p class="mt-4">
            When we're not coding or training AI models, you might find us exploring the beautiful trails around St. Louis, keeping up with the latest tech trends, or brainstorming innovative solutions for our next project.
          </p>
  
          <div class="mt-12">
            
              <a href="#contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 text-base font-medium text-white bg-blue-600 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
            >
              Let's Work Together
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="w-5 h-5"
                viewBox="0 0 20 20"
                fill="currentColor"
              >
                <path
                  fill-rule="evenodd"
                  d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
                  clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>